Fred G. ZERBST, Warden of the United States Penitentiary at Leavenworth, Kansas, v. Allen HENRATTY. No. 1250. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. April 22, 1935. S. S. Alexander, U. S. Atty., of Topeka, Kan., for appellant. Calvin, Vandeventer & .Kimbrell, of Kansas City, Mo., for appellee.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal (9 F. Supp. 230) dismissed on motion of appellant.
